channel.description:
[center]
[IMG]http://i65.tinypic.com/2gvn78p.png[/img]
Age Of Chaos Introduction
On the 20th of December 2016,me and friend have decided to start work on our own server. We're learning as we go along, and we know we're nowhere near the best server and will never claim to be so. So far, we're doing pretty well. We've tried to create an economy server where coins have a value, where skillers can actually make money by supplying the items demanded by the PvM players. This also means that not everything is available by shops,giving lots of items value with profit to always be made if there is a demand. Age Of Chaos, so far, has been a good learning experience and, best of all, great fun. To this date, we've completed over 100 updates.
Achievements play a big part our server, with a huge range of accomplishments players can reach for, whether it be collecting the 50+ boss pets, achieving all 120s/200M skills and even 5b capes, trimmed completionist, prestige 10, or even maxing an insane XP account, there is always another challenge waiting for you!
Age Of Chaos developers are working effortlessly to insure the server is the best it can be, ensuring our content looks clean to its players, making us unique in how we bring our content. We limit the use of :: commands, we ensure items have correct models and that we do not release half-assed content. Every update has the economy and value of current items in mind.
Age Of Chaos is powered by our community,the reason being our motto is "The Players Server!", this means that all our updates and hard work will be for the players this way the players can count on us as server developers knowing that we will not quit them we will give them the best experience we possibly can.
Thanks for reading our Introduction.
Age Of Chaos in-game features
- Every skill trainable, including FULL construction with house creation, dungeons, floors, combat rings, altars etc.
- Daily tasks that scale to your levels with rewards and provide huge variety. Over 300 skilling tasks alone, all handled via one enum.
- Clan chat system, with customization, guest chats, logos, etc.
- Clean Grand Exchange with no search lag, prices changing etc.
- Squeal of Fortune (awards daily spins, accounts for spin types, etc).
- 80+ pets obtainable (approximately 40 of which are boss pets).
- Achievement rewards, such as real RS3 master capes, max cape, completionist and trimmed completionist capes with the ability to create hooded max/comp/trim capes!
- Challenging and rewarding bosses.including vorago! and many more!
- Tier 90 gear: malevolent, drygores, sirenic, ascensions, tectonic, seismic, ROtS shields, noxious longbow.
- Dual wielding with CLEAN sheathing (no command - done via appearance data): low level magic wands, Ahrim's, Virtus, dragon, chaotics, ascensions, drygores, seismics.
- Achievement trackers for bosses, clue scrolls and barrows and even different points such as pvm points trivia points ect.
- Charming imp and boss pets system.
- Trivia system with new questions regularly, maximum five answers per question and point shop with rewards.
- 95% farming including leprechauns noting supplies etc. Also accompanied by an almost complete lunar spell book (a few spells left to do).
- Five tier prestige system, with tier 85 ports armors available in fifth prestige shop.
- Notes fully working with color change text
- Many mini-games such as Hunger games,duel arena,castle wars,fist of guthix,dominion tower and many more!
- Plenty of account secrurity including the command ::securemac for making you account only acssesable by your mac address we also have a ::secureip if you use more then one device at home.
We have plenty of more content we would say this is the most content packed 718 loading 751 server our there come and play today to see our great server with an awesome community.
Hope to see you guys in-game soon!
GreekO.
DEVELOPERS/OWNERS
- GreekO - - WarlocK -
